{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870910/extras/Frame_1.gif?t=1711009431\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Welcome to Largo!</h2>Largo is a game in the style of <strong>I'm on Observation Duty</strong>, where you monitor security cameras and spot differences in various locations.<br><br>Enter a world with an eerie post-apocalyptic atmosphere where humanity has disappeared without a trace. As a survivor, your task is to examine different abandoned and liminal spaces, and report anomalies.<br><br>Stay vigilant for unexpected guests and make it through to dawn!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Report hundreds of anomalies across four dilapidated settings: an arctic log cabin, an office space, a supermarket and an opera house<br></li><li> Click on objects to file a report<br></li><li> Select from four levels of difficulty<br></li><li> Encounter a wide array of anomalies, from the easily noticeable to those that are incredibly subtle<br></li><li> Face entities in various spine-chilling scenarios<br></li><li> Earn Steam Achievements for conquering the Nightmare mode and reporting Special Anomalies</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Punched out!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2870910/76b9a47cd99fd1055318f297441fcfb9bc1ef50a.jpg"},{"name":"Boss Fight!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2870910/6526c8d772fa17f7a21b31bd9282b0dcf8491765.jpg"},{"name":"Gold Medal!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2870910/81316a17e0eab7634a42edaa29ff5075ef63c665.jpg"},{"name":"Winter is over!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2870910/6b6edbe7886704a784fd2375e2c15edf1c090f68.jpg"},{"name":"Master survivor!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2870910/c5770b7026670da8968